reviewText: Rob Bell's nooma video "Shells" is great at challenging Christian leaders to look at the busyness of their lives and really think about what is important in one's life and what can be dropped. Bell's message helps to refocus one's life priorities and vocational choices on God. It was thoughtful, reflective, and God-centered.
I think I'll stick to Rob's books....they are only $2 more and last more than 10 minutes.
